 Planning, implementing and releasing production changes using zero-downtime techniques
 Empowering engineers to contribute changes to infrastructure by pairing, supporting and mentoring
 Conducting root cause analysis and identifying relationships between processes and events
 Performing ongoing design and code reviews
 Participating in 24/7 on-call rotation (weekly rotation, primary/secondary)
